人當透明，好彩我個gip好細又唔在意依個格差待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後中間都係受類似對待，俾人騷擾，男朋友同我買條頭巾包下個頭，然後就少咗呢啲情況出現，全程都唔暴露拖鞋都冇著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47faebfaec611231d4e170fc678abffded7858c","tid":372450,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T21:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明想睇片班人乜野心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇字見到咁慘已經於心不忍</blockquote><br />\n班垃圾"},{"pid":"65344f19916d7650d1115355e9ca9931fc04b82b","tid":372450,"uid":109589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T22:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/064638_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F064638_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c5fd0dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新聞報緊"},{"pid":"1f1c472769d1b614fb9f9c277aeae18a4a70704f","tid":372450,"uid":29270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T23:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">有網民指該名女子是咎由自取，指她不應登上有這多男乘客的巴士</span><br />\n<br />\n弱智低劣人種</blockquote><br />\n摩洛哥連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3d6fa2554c27aed78bb7c6168d16c4155454ad","tid":372450,"uid":18647,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T23:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解個女仔俾人非禮揸波仲拍埋片都有人求seed求片 個女仔俾幾個畜牲搞咁陰功有咩好睇 屌你地前世未睇過女人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有上面班垃圾連登仔就話喺手機面前j下算姐 班乘客居然真係冇人出黎幫個女仔 好撚心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母啦 睇片就係打j 架咩<br />\n死撚左去啦道德撚"},{"pid":"a2809bf959a70d234d4a4e23d76d78e6e45a413e","tid":372450,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T23:51:54.000Z","msg":"班友睇av睇到short 左<img src=\"/assets/f